- 'Graph type' refers to a category or species in the metaphorical forest;
- 'Work' is metaphorically considered as the effort or energy required to optimize, similar to the effort needed to maintain a species' ecosystem in a forest;
- 'Average work' symbolizes the mean effort required to keep each species well-maintained in the forest.
